OL,6,FNHS unions have reached a pay deal with
OL,7,Fthe Government, potentially ending the
OL,8,Flong-running dispute that led to
OL,9,Fhistoric strike action.
OL,11,FThe offer, which includes a one-off
OL,12,Fpayment for the 2022/23 financial year,
OL,13,Fplus a 5 per cent pay rise for 2023/24,
OL,14,Fwill apply to NHS staff including
OL,15,Fnurses, paramedics, 999 call handlers,
OL,16,Fmidwives, healthcare assistants,
OL,17,Fsecurity guards and cleaners.
OL,19,FIt does not apply to junior doctors,
OL,20,Fwho are involved in a separate dispute.
